OL,5,G2200 Michael Palin in Nigeria
OL,6,     FIn the first leg of an epic 1300
OL,7,     Fmiles across Nigeria, Michael is
OL,8,     Fin bustling Lagos and an
OL,9,     Fextraordinary waterfront slum
OL,10,     Fschool, then dodges alligators at
OL,11,     Fthe Emir of Kano's palace. (Ep1/3)
OL,12,G2305 Prisoner: Cell Block H
